# Cloudflare Pages headers — see https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/
#
# COEP intentionally OMITTED for now. The earlier `require-corp` value blocked
# Pyodide's micropip fetches from PyPI on mobile (PyPI doesn't set CORP), which
# manifested as an "engine crash" after the page loaded. Pyodide doesn't need
# SharedArrayBuffer for v0.1; if M5/M6 needs SAB for fast worker→main numpy
# transfers, switch to `Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: credentialless` (Chrome/
# Firefox/Edge support it; Safari needs `require-corp` + a fetch proxy).

/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin

/*.js
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=3600

/css/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=3600

/models/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=86400, immutable
